import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.hist(data['x'], bins=50, color='green')
    plt.axvline(data['x'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Mean: {data['x'].mean():0.2f}")
    plt.axvline(data['x'].median(), color='blue', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label=f"Median: {data['x'].median():0.2f}")
    plt.xlabel('x')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of x?')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.hist(data['y'], bins=20, color='green')

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.scatter(data['saturation'], data['lumosity'], c=data['lumosity'], cmap='viridis')
    plt.xlabel('Saturation')
    plt.ylabel('Lumosity')
    plt.title('What is the relationship between lumosity and saturation?')
    plt.colorbar(label='Lumosity')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    name_frequencies = data['name'].value_counts()
    ax = name_frequencies.plot(kind='bar', color=['#1f77b4', '#ff7f0e', '#2ca02c'])
    ax.axhline(y=name_frequencies.max(), color='r', linestyle='--', label='Max frequency: {:.2f}'.format(name_frequencies.max()))
    ax.legend()
    plt.title('What are the most common names in the dataset?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Name')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.xticks(rotation=0)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    color_counts = data['color'].value_counts()
    color_counts.plot(kind='bar', color=color_counts.index, legend=False)
    plt.xlabel('Color')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of color values?')
    for i, count in enumerate(color_counts):
        plt.text(i, count, str(count), ha='center', va='bottom')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
